I think more generic names would be better as this is to Binance-specific
some exchanges have a flat structure with many account for a given currency and no master
I would suggest:
    /**
     * Withdrawal from the exchange a blockchain address or a bank account.
     *
     * Usually results in a withdrawal fee being subtracted
     */
    WITHDRAWAL(false),

    /** Deposit from a blockchain address or a bank account to the exchange */
    DEPOSIT(true),

    /** Used for transfers between exchanges accounts */
    INTERNAL_WITHDRAWAL(false);

    /** Used for transfers between exchanges accounts */
    INTERNAL_DEPOSIT(true),

    /** Used for transfers between exchanges accounts */
    INTERNAL_WITHDRAWAL(false);
